{
  "chapter": 18,
  "chapter_summary": "本章围绕阿吉的真实身份展开暗流涌动的心理博弈。铁虎登门韩大奶奶的青楼，以冷静缜密的分析推断阿吉并非寻常人物，而是某个本应已死的绝顶高手。他命令韩大奶奶将阿吉带来，韩大奶奶表面应承内心恐惧。场景转向哑巴厨子的破旧小屋，阿吉与哑巴夫妇饮酒叙情，展现了底层人物之间质朴温暖的友情。韩大奶奶闯入告知铁虎来访之事，阿吉虽知危险临近仍因友情破戒饮酒。韩大奶奶最终透露铁虎已猜出阿吉是\"本应已死之人\"，阿吉淡然以对。全章通过铁虎的深沉、韩大奶奶的周旋和阿吉的沉默，层层铺垫即将到来的决战。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "没有好处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "因为他不为你挨那几刀，你还是一样对他的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "我怎么样对他，他根本也不太在乎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "他不惜为了苗子兄妹跟大老板拼命，对他又有什么好处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "没有好处！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "像他这样的人，怎么会做出见不得人的事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他这么样做，一定是受了某种打击，忽然间对一切事都变得心灰意冷，他不惜忍受痛苦和羞辱，一定是因为他的家世和声名太显赫，现在他既然已变成这样子，就绝不能再让别人知道他的过去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 17,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "其实你用不着为他担心的！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹譯",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "他一出手就杀了铁头，毁了铁手，竟连一点本门功夫都没有露出来，武功能练到这种地步的，我想来想去都不会超出五个人，像他这样年纪的，很可能只有一个！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "是哪一个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 49,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "那个人本来已经死了，可是我一直都认为他绝不会死得那么快！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "你认为阿吉就是他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "如果阿吉真的就是那个人，这一战死的就必定是我！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "那么你为什么一定要去为别人拼命？为什么一定要找他？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "我并不一定要去。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "可是另外一个人却一定要去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "你！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "你要我去找阿吉？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "去带他来见我！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "我怎么知道他的人在哪里？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "你应该知道的，因为他现在只有一个地方可去！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "什么地方？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 81,
      "line_end": 81
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "这里！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "他为什么一定会到这里来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "因为他已跟大老板约好了，今天晚上在这里相见，他当然一定会先来看看这里的情况，看看大老板是不是会布下什么埋伏陷阱？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "城里只有这里是他最熟悉的，这里的每个人好像都对他不错，他可以随便找个地方躲起来，大老板的人一定找不到他，如果是我，也一定会这么样做的！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 91,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "可惜他不是虎大爷，他没有虎大爷这么精明详细！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "虎大爷若是不相信，可以随便去搜。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "这地方虎大爷岂非熟得很？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 101
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_hu",
      "speaker_name": "铁虎",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "他真的没有来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 103,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_tie_hu",
      "text": "他若来了，我怎么会不知？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_qi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴妻子",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "这不是好酒，但却是真的酒，哑巴知道你喜欢喝酒！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_qi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴妻子",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你为什么不喝？我们的酒虽然不好，至少总不是偷来的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_ba_qi_zi",
      "speaker_name": "哑巴妻子",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "哑巴想告诉你，你肯喝他的酒，就表示你看得起他，把他当做好朋友，好兄弟！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你又在喝酒？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "喝了一点！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你自己应该知道今天不该喝酒的，为什么还要喝？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "因为哑巴是我的朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "朋友，朋友一斤能值多少钱？难道比自己的命还珍贵？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "铁虎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "你知不知道他是个怎么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "是个很厉害的人！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "不但厉害，而且远比你想像中还厉害得多！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "他不但算准了你一定在这里，而且还猜出了你是谁。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "是个本来已经应该死了的人！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_ji",
      "speaker_name": "阿吉",
      "listener": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "text": "我现在还活着。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_da_nai_nai",
      "speaker_name": "韩大奶奶",
      "listener": "char_a_ji",
      "text": "他也不相信你已死了，可是我相信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 18,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    }
  ],
